{"pageProps":{"metadata":{"title":"Python基礎文法 - 後期","curriculumId":"1ada501e-f337-81d0-93c4-cc25006a2031","category":"後期","visibility":["基礎班","発展班"],"tags":["基礎班","Python"],"is_basic_curriculum":true,"id":"108"},"mdBlocks":[{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81f4-84a0-cfa6ac62e75c","type":"paragraph","parent":"今回はpythonの`lambda`式について説明します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8128-86c7-fb7018a46ea4","type":"heading_2","parent":"## lambda式の基本","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-819f-b278-f5a2b95f6626","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8113-9f68-f3c897b4e205","type":"paragraph","parent":"`lambda`式は、関数を作るための短縮記法です。通常の関数定義と異なり、`lambda`式は一行で書け、関数名を省略することができます。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8129-95ef-eb218ca9061c","type":"callout","parent":"> 基本構文  \n> ```python  \n> lambda 引数:処理内容  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8184-9caf-f995239fa89e","type":"code","parent":"```python\nlambda 引数:処理内容\n```","children":[]}]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8163-ba78-eb70655b3e4a","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- **引数**: 関数に渡す引数。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8180-bc34-c9d27c903e58","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- **式**: 関数が返す結果（通常、1つの式のみ）。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8164-ac17-eab7c8cfe855","type":"paragraph","parent":"引数がない場合は引数の部分に`_`（アンダーバー）を使います","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81fe-9de6-d8855194fbf8","type":"callout","parent":"> 引数がない場合  \n> ```python  \n> lambda _:処理内容  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81f1-a220-c13428232bf9","type":"code","parent":"```python\nlambda _:処理内容\n```","children":[]}]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81f5-b3d3-c420cb2567c2","type":"heading_2","parent":"## 使用例","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81d0-bd74-e9aad1f548e4","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8103-9070-d787ac688a15","type":"paragraph","parent":"lambda式の具体的な使用例を示します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81b3-a2e7-fc32f88f39c0","type":"callout","parent":"> 2つの引数を受け取って、その和を返す関数  \n> ```python  \n> add = lambda x, y: x + y  \n> print(add(3, 5))  # 8  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81c6-82f8-f36c9e8215cd","type":"code","parent":"```python\nadd = lambda x, y: x + y\nprint(add(3, 5))  # 8\n```","children":[]}]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81e2-8317-dae651b2de99","type":"callout","parent":"> リスト内の各要素を2倍にする関数  \n> ```python  \n> nums = [1, 2, 3, 4]  \n> doubled = list(map(lambda x: x * 2, nums))  \n> print(doubled)  # [2, 4, 6, 8]  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8180-abcb-f5af04dba74e","type":"code","parent":"```python\nnums = [1, 2, 3, 4]\ndoubled = list(map(lambda x: x * 2, nums))\nprint(doubled)  # [2, 4, 6, 8]\n```","children":[]}]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81b7-9f84-fb41426d8380","type":"paragraph","parent":"","children":[]}],"pageNavs":[{"title":"Home","id":"/posts"},{"title":"基礎班カリキュラム","id":"/posts/course/basic"},{"title":"後期","id":"/posts/course/後期"},{"title":"Python基礎文法 - 後期","id":"/posts/curriculums/1ada501e-f337-81d0-93c4-cc25006a2031/1ada501e-f337-81d0-93c4-cc25006a2031"},{"id":"/posts/curriculums/1ada501e-f337-81d0-93c4-cc25006a2031/1ada501e-f337-81ec-b2e6-e054e5b77d29","title":"lambda式"}],"childrenData":{"title":"Python基礎文法 - 後期","childPages":[{"title":"import文","id":"1ada501e-f337-8176-9896-f0815ebd1e1c"},{"title":"クラスの継承","id":"1ada501e-f337-8139-983b-df7225049e88"},{"title":"文字列の中に変数を埋め込む","id":"1ada501e-f337-812d-a298-f72af5ac68d6"},{"title":"lambda式","id":"1ada501e-f337-81ec-b2e6-e054e5b77d29"},{"title":"例外処理","id":"1ada501e-f337-81f8-bf0d-eb68b3253fce"}]},"pageId":"1ada501e-f337-81ec-b2e6-e054e5b77d29","title":"lambda式"},"__N_SSG":true}